CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 9, 1956, p. 15, reads: "AKA Sorors - Initiated into Iota Chapter of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority were Leebertha West, Leebrun [LeeBrun] Johnson, Rosalie Travis, Alma Frazier, Helen Adair, Carmenita Austin and Dorothy Nelson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Kappa Alpha sorority initiates Leebertha West, LeeBrun Johnson, Rosalie Travis, Alma Frazier, Helen Adair, Carmenita Austin, and Dorothy Nelson posed on stairs in Greene Hearth
